creator: Hivency
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the heart of web influence ! Join our shopping platform dedicated to influencers 🙈

Receive free products, like 50 000 influencers already on our platform

How it works :
- Discover products/service offered by our partners brand (Beauty, Fashion, Food, Events, Design, ect.)
- Order the ones you like the most
- If you match with the brand, you'll be sent the product/service in exchange for a post on your social network.

The registration on Hivency is open to EVERYONE, no matter how many followers or views you have !
By way of indication, here are criterias from which, generally, our brands will start to offer their products/services.
- 5,000 followers on Instagram (Only public profile will be able to receive products/services.)
- 1,000 views per video on Youtube
- 1,000 views per Snapchat story
- 5,000 views per month on your blog.

As we grow, we have more or more offers which are available below these criterias.
If you're not reaching them yet, do not hesitate to give it a try !

Any question ? Write to us at hello@hivency.com
